(7, 'Talend Data Integration for Beginners – Job Oriented Program', 'One Stop & Easy Learning Solution for Talend Data Integration', '<p>Talend is a powerful and versatile open source solution that addresses all of an organization’s data integration needs.</p>\n<p>This session for Talend Data Integration Tool has been designed for beginners who are aspiring to work in Business Intelligence &amp; ETL technologies and earn handsome salary. This course can also be taken by those who wants to upgrade their skills and learn Talend Data Integration tool and look for new opportunities. This course has step by step process of learning Talend data integration Tool.</p>\n<p>We have also added comprehensive data warehousing session to help student understand Business intelligence, ETL processes and different data processing mechanism.</p>\n<p>This entire course has been divided into 12 different sections which covers all aspects of Talend Data Integration Learning Program. This entire program is having 26+ hours of lectures with complete demo in each and every section covering almost all important sections of Talend Data Integration Tools.</p>\n<p>There are 100+ Interview questions, assignments &amp; scenarios to support students who are looking for new opportunities in Talend.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Thank You &amp; Happy Learning!</p>\n', 2500000, 43, 4.6, 8278, 11, 235, '2021-07-26', 0, '2021-01-08', 0, 92632, 0, 'https://myedu-1612407.s3.sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/11/courses/1610566689416-cntt.jpg', 'talend-data-integration-for-beginners---job-oriented-program');
