(13, 'Lập trình Machine Learning cơ bản với Python', 'Learn how to build powerful and valuable machine learning models in Python. Code templates included.', '<p></p>\n<p>Interested in the field of Machine Learning? Then this course is for you!</p>\n<p>This course was designed by two professional data scientists who share their expertise to help you integrate the perfect intuition of Machine Learning models and give you the skills to implement these models.</p>\n<p>Everything will be done step by step so that you develop your understanding of Machine Learning in a clear and progressive way. Each tutorial will teach you a new skill and a new solid foundation.</p>\n<p>We will build models to solve business problems based on real world scenarios. You will learn how to take advantage of Machine Learning to create added value in these business issues.</p>\n<p>This course is divided into 4 parts, each corresponding to a fundamental branch of Machine Learning:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Part 1 - Data Preprocessing: to properly prepare the data so as to facilitate the learning of the model.</li>\n<li>Part 2 - Regression: to predict a continuous real value.</li>\n<li>Part 3 - Classification: to predict a category.</li>\n<li>Part 4 - Clustering: to identify segments of observations grouped by similarity.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>And as a bonus, this course includes all the code templates for implementing Machine Learning models in the general case, so that you can use them very easily on your datasets.</p>\n<p></p>\n<h2>Who is this course for?</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Anyone interested in Machine Learning</li>\n<li>Anyone interested in Artificial Intelligence</li>\n<li>Anyone aiming for a career as a data scientist</li>\n<li>Anyone wishing to make a difference by acquiring the \"Machine Learning\" skill</li>\n</ul>\n', 1750000, 42, 4.5, 7010, 2, 159, '2021-07-20', 0, '2021-01-11', 0, 58768, 1, 'https://myedu-1612407.s3.sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/2/courses/1610568061721-2_com.png', 'lap-trinh-machine-learning-