(17, 'Lập trình Front - End cơ bản với Landing Page', 'Become an expert in web development with Front-End techs: HTML, CSS, Javascript, Jquery.', '<h2>Prerequisite</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>You will not need any special knowledge.</li>\n<li>You will need a free editor (included in the course)</li>\n<li>A cool browser (also included in the course)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Description</h2>\n<p>Hi ! Welcome to the complete <strong>Front-End course</strong>  will allow you to become a web integrator very easily. With my experience as a web trainer, I designed this course to be the only one you need to become a front-end developer.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>This course has been designed by a  <strong>professional</strong> independent <strong>trainer</strong></li>\n<li>You will all learn what I <strong>use every day</strong> as a <strong>Front-end Developer</strong></li>\n<li>The course only contains Front-End technology so <strong>no PHP</strong> and other server approaches.</li>\n<li>Each section contains a <strong>summary exercise</strong> .</li>\n<li><strong>Each month</strong> the course will be updated to add a Full Front-End project.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>This course is being written and  <strong>will evolve into a Front-End Developer course. </strong></p>\n<p><strong>Coming soon, the </strong><strong><em>JQuery</em></strong><strong> module and a corrected professional project FREE for those who have already purchased this course!</strong></p>\n<h2>Who is this course for?</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Everyone interested in a career in Front-End development</li>\n<li>Beginner developers who want to learn HTML, CSS, and javascript</li>\n<li>Confirmed developers wanting to gain Front-End expertise</li>\n<li>This course does not cover the back-end developer part.</li>\n<li>Understand the code and make changes yourself</li>\n</ul>\n', 4100000, 47, 4.1, 6004, 11, 251, '2021-07-20', 0, '2021-01-11', 0, 54323, 1, 'https://myedu-1612407.s3.sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/11/courses/1610568379573-images (1).jpg', 'lap-trinh-front